---
title: Saucy Ragù Pasta with  Beyond Meat®  and Olive Tapenade
description: This twist on classic spaghetti Bolognese is a winner! Penne replaces spaghetti, and the ragù is packed with Beyond Meat® and tons of flavour. Topped with fresh olive tapenade, this dish will have everyone coming back for seconds!
